gobblin.util.request_allocation

Interface HierarchicalPrioritizer<T extends Request>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparator<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleHierarchicalPrioritizer

    public interface HierarchicalPrioritizer<T extends Request>
extends Comparator<T>
    A Comparator for Requests that can also compare Requestors, and which guarantees that given Requests r1, r2, then r1.getRequestor > r2.getRequestor implies r1 > r2.
